range_spray by GloStiX

i just made this in hammer in like 1/2 an hour so i could prep for my OGL match. lol.
it basically is an aim map with every weapon and 4 targets. you should use:

sv_cheats 1
impulse 101
sv_showimpacts 1

that way, you will be able to have full ammo in every weapon, and you can see where
your bullets are hitting.

this map is meant for personal practice use, etc.--not for competitive playing.

thanks and have fun
